Package org.apache.shardingsphere.sql.parser.autogen

Interface MySQLStatementVisitor<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MySQLDALStatementVisitor, MySQLDCLStatementVisitor, MySQLDDLStatementVisitor, MySQLDMLStatementVisitor, MySQLFormatVisitor, MySQLRLStatementVisitor, MySQLStatementBaseVisitor, MySQLStatementVisitor, MySQLTCLStatementVisitor
    public interface MySQLStatementVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by MySQLStatementParser.
